```python
costPer100ms = 0.0000016667
costPerMs = costPer100ms / 100
timePerCallS = 40
timePerCallMs = timePerCallS * 1000
costPerCall = costPerMs * timePerCallMs
callsPerDay = 60 * 24 /10
costPerDay = callsPerDay * costPerCall
```
